<s> Here's some proposed text to consider adding to section 7.6 if we lean towards option 3 above (note this would also require changing the text in the above quoted paragraphs):  </s>
<s> Servers MAY restrict usage of the lock token to exactly the authenticated principal who created the lock.  </s>
<s> Servers MAY also allow other privileged authenticated principals or even unauthenticated principals to use the lock token.  </s>
